Nungua bụ obodo dị na Krowor Municipal District na Greater Accra Region nke ndịda ọwụwa anyanwụ Ghana nso n'ụsọ oké osimiri
Nungua bụ obodo nke iri na asatọ kacha nwee ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ na Ghana, n'ihe gbasara ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ, nwere mmadụ 84,119
Nungua dị n'ime Krowor Constituency nke Agnes Naa Momo Lartey, onye otu National Democratic Congress, onye nọchiri Elizabeth Afoley Quaye nke New Patriotic Party.
Ha nọ na agbụrụ asatọ, ya bụ: Nii Mantse We, Nii Moi We, Nii Borte We, Nii Adzin Anyị, Nii Borkwei We, Nii Osokrono Anyị, Nii Odarteitse Anyị, na Nii Djenge Anyị
Onye isi nke Nungua bụ Eze (Dr) Odaifio Welentsi III.
Enwere ike ịnweta agụmakwụkwọ na ọkwa niile na Nungua
